I cut the mute cable on a 12-820 and had it cycle through.  Every so
often, it&#39;ll still lock on a random channel for like a second or so
and then start the sweep again.  On one of the FM sweeps it actually
locked in on a &quot;not in tune&quot; channel permanently. Anyone else have
this happen?

Marty

    
